Simple application to read current clocks of ATi Radeon cards (xf86-video-ati)
Install lm_sensors for gpu temperature.

App need to be run with root privilages for read clocks and changing profiles.

# Dependencies
* debugfs enabled¹
* qt4
* opensource radeon drivers

¹) no values?: mount -t debugfs none /sys/kernel/debug`

# For full funcionality:
* glxinfo - info about OpenGL, mesa
* xdriinfo - driver info
* xrandr - connected displays
* lm_sensors² - temperature

²) no need if hwmon for card is present in sysfs


https://github.com/marazmista/radeon-profile